00:16:35.445 --> 00:16:39.716
But, the assumptions that we must make,

406
00:16:39.716 --> 00:16:42.686
for a travel narrative to make meaning,

407
00:16:42.686 --> 00:16:45.492
is that there is space and time.

408
00:16:45.492 --> 00:16:47.441
<v Regina>Right.</v>
<v ->So, how can you,</v>

409
00:16:47.441 --> 00:16:49.761
you see it's really,

